entity.name: Keeley Jones
entity.text:
Keeley Jones is a main regular character featured in the Apple TV+ show, Ted Lasso, a model-turned-PR consultant for AFC Richmond, an ex-girlfriend of Roy Kent, a best friend of Rebecca Welton, a good friend of Ted Lasso, an ex-girlfriend of Jamie Tartt, a good friend of Flo Collins, and a CEO of KJPR Firm in Richmond. [...] Keeley is a freethinking woman with an entrepreneurial spirit who made a name for herself as an Influencer and a (often topless) model. She claims she is "sort of famous for being almost famous". A Richmond fan named Tommy even claims that Keeley was a "seminal" figure of his teenage years instead of Roy who was more famous.

## Contents [...] After Roy retired from football, Keeley is very keen for him to make something of his career, including taking up an offer from Sky Sports as a pundit on TV. Around this time, Keeley and Roy also go on a double date with Rebecca and John Wingsnight. After the double date, Rebecca asks what do they think about her date, but Roy gives a passionate speech about how she shouldn't settle with a boring nice man. She should be with someone who makes her feel like being struck by a lightning. His
